SELECT u.full_name, p.vein_pattern, a.log_id FROM user_profiles u JOIN palm_vein_data p ON u.user_id = p.user_id JOIN access_logs a ON u.user_id = a.user_id WHERE u.age > 30 ORDER BY u.full_name DESC;
SELECT pv.id, pv.vein_pattern, pm.match_score FROM palm_vein_data pv JOIN palm_vein_matches pm ON pv.id = pm.target_id WHERE pm.match_score > 80 ORDER BY pm.match_score DESC;

SELECT u.full_name, p.vein_pattern, a.action FROM user_profiles u JOIN palm_vein_data p ON u.user_id = p.user_id JOIN access_logs a ON u.user_id = a.user_id WHERE a.access_time BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31' ORDER BY a.access_time ASC;
